{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01EZGfaUX9rVa4duMvdjNFfw","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_012jd8hRpkVJpgQZ84QvSvDZ","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"\\\ngit add scripts/release/cargo-publish-if-new.sh scripts/tests/test_cargo_publish_if_new.sh && \\\ngit commit -m \"fix(ci): make cargo-publish-if-new fail-closed on malformed registry JSON\n\nFINDING 1 (medium): registry_has_version() was fail-open — when crates.io\nreturns HTTP 200 with a non-JSON body, jq silently exits non-zero, the\nversion lookup falls through to 'not found' (return 1), and the helper\nproceeds to cargo publish, which then fails with a duplicate-version error.\n\nFix: add a jq parse-validation step immediately after curl succeeds, before\nthe version lookup. If the body is not parseable JSON, print a 'registry\nreturned malformed JSON' diagnostic to stderr and return 2 (error), same\nexit code as the existing curl-failure path. Fail-closed.\n\nFINDING 2 (low): all decision-case tests injected CARGO_PUBLISH_IF_NEW_LOCAL_VERSION,\nbypassing resolve_local_version() entirely. Neither code path was covered.\n\nFix: add two manifest-reader tests that invoke the helper WITHOUT the env-var\nbypass, driving resolve_local_version() against real repo manifests (read-only):\n  - test 9: fathomdb-embedder-api (inline version = \\\"0.6.0\\\") → skip\n  - test 10: fathomdb-engine (version.workspace = true → 0.6.1) → publish\n\nTDD RED: test 8 failed before the helper fix (rc=0, cargo invoked) confirming\nthe fail-open bug. Tests 9-10 passed, confirming existing manifest reader\ncorrectness. All 10 tests GREEN after fix.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\"","description":"Commit the fix and tests"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":159,"cache_read_input_tokens":29942,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":159},"output_tokens":53,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"94ef9a18-efe7-461e-91d9-252b6b93035c","uuid":"7836780b-e808-49d6-bf3c-27afe57cd50b","request_id":"req_011CbNQmz3TVku6PunQ8Quer"}
